{
  "texts": [
    "ToolLLaMA, an LLM fine-tuned from LLaMA [285], exhibits remarkable zero-shot capabilities and performance comparable to state-of-the-art LLMs like ChatGPT [209].",
    "(3) Factuality Evaluation.",
    "TruthfulQA [164] measures the truthfulness of language models in answering questions.",
    "This benchmark consists of 817 questions covering 38 categories, including health, law, finance, and politics.",
    "This evaluation reveals that, even in optimal conditions, the truthfulness of model responses only reaches 58%, in stark contrast to human performance at 94%."
  ]
}